<div class="container" x-data="{ open: {} }">

  <header>
    <a href="/" class="back-link">&larr; Kembali ke Beranda</a>
    <h1>Dokumentasi Fuzzy Logic</h1>
    <p>Penjelasan lengkap sistem inferensi fuzzy untuk penyiraman tanaman</p>
  </header>

  <!-- 1. Gambaran Umum -->
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-header" @click="open['overview'] = !open['overview']">
      <h2>1. Gambaran Umum</h2>
      <span class="section-arrow" :style="open['overview'] ? 'transform:rotate(90deg)' : ''">&#9654;</span>
    </div>
    <div class="section-body" x-show="open['overview']" x-collapse>
      <p>
        Sistem ini menggunakan <strong>Fuzzy Logic metode Mamdani</strong> untuk menentukan
        durasi penyiraman tanaman secara otomatis. Keputusan didasarkan pada 4 variabel input
        dan menghasilkan 1 variabel output.
      </p>
      <p>Alur proses inferensi fuzzy:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Fuzzifikasi</strong> &mdash; mengubah nilai crisp (tegas) menjadi derajat keanggotaan fuzzy</li>
        <li><strong>Evaluasi Aturan</strong> &mdash; mengevaluasi seluruh aturan IF-THEN menggunakan operator AND (minimum)</li>
        <li><strong>Agregasi</strong> &mdash; menggabungkan hasil semua aturan menggunakan operator MAX</li>
        <li><strong>Defuzzifikasi</strong> &mdash; mengubah himpunan fuzzy output menjadi nilai crisp menggunakan metode Centroid</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 2. Variabel Input -->
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-header" @click="open['inputs'] = !open['inputs']">
      <h2>2. Variabel Input</h2>
      <span class="section-arrow" :style="open['inputs'] ? 'transform:rotate(90deg)' : ''">&#9654;</span>
    </div>
    <div class="section-body" x-show="open['inputs']" x-collapse>
      <p>Sistem menerima 4 variabel input. Tiga dari sensor dan satu dari API BMKG.</p>

      <div class="subsection">
        <h3>2.1 Kelembapan Tanah (0 &ndash; 1023)</h3>
        <p>Nilai analog dari sensor kelembapan tanah. Semakin tinggi nilainya, semakin basah tanahnya.</p>
        <table class="data-table">
          <thead><tr><th>Himpunan</th><th>Tipe</th><th>Parameter</th><th>Rentang Penuh</th></tr></thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr><td>Kering (<em>dry</em>)</td><td>Trapezoidal</td><td>(0, 0, 200, 400)</td><td>0 &ndash; 400</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Lembap (<em>moist</em>)</td><td>Triangular</td><td>(300, 500, 700)</td><td>300 &ndash; 700</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Basah (<em>wet</em>)</td><td>Trapezoidal</td><td>(600, 800, 1023, 1023)</td><td>600 &ndash; 1023</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <div class="subsection">
        <h3>2.2 Suhu Udara (&deg;C)</h3>
        <table class="data-table">
          <thead><tr><th>Himpunan</th><th>Tipe</th><th>Parameter</th><th>Rentang Penuh</th></tr></thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr><td>Sejuk (<em>cool</em>)</td><td>Trapezoidal</td><td>(0, 0, 18, 25)</td><td>0 &ndash; 25</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Hangat (<em>warm</em>)</td><td>Triangular</td><td>(22, 28, 34)</td><td>22 &ndash; 34</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Panas (<em>hot</em>)</td><td>Trapezoidal</td><td>(32, 38, 50, 50)</td><td>32 &ndash; 50</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <div class="subsection">
        <h3>2.3 Kelembapan Udara (0 &ndash; 100%)</h3>
        <table class="data-table">
          <thead><tr><th>Himpunan</th><th>Tipe</th><th>Parameter</th><th>Rentang Penuh</th></tr></thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr><td>Rendah (<em>low</em>)</td><td>Trapezoidal</td><td>(0, 0, 25, 45)</td><td>0 &ndash; 45</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Sedang (<em>medium</em>)</td><td>Triangular</td><td>(35, 55, 75)</td><td>35 &ndash; 75</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Tinggi (<em>high</em>)</td><td>Trapezoidal</td><td>(65, 80, 100, 100)</td><td>65 &ndash; 100</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <div class="subsection">
        <h3>2.4 Curah Hujan / Presipitasi (mm)</h3>
        <p>Total presipitasi dalam 3 jam ke depan, diambil otomatis dari API BMKG.</p>
        <table class="data-table">
          <thead><tr><th>Himpunan</th><th>Tipe</th><th>Parameter</th><th>Rentang Penuh</th></tr></thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr><td>Tidak Ada (<em>none</em>)</td><td>Trapezoidal</td><td>(0, 0, 0.1, 0.5)</td><td>0 &ndash; 0.5</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Ringan (<em>light</em>)</td><td>Triangular</td><td>(0.3, 1.5, 4)</td><td>0.3 &ndash; 4</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Lebat (<em>heavy</em>)</td><td>Trapezoidal</td><td>(3, 6, 50, 50)</td><td>3 &ndash; 50</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 3. Variabel Output -->
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-header" @click="open['output'] = !open['output']">
      <h2>3. Variabel Output</h2>
      <span class="section-arrow" :style="open['output'] ? 'transform:rotate(90deg)' : ''">&#9654;</span>
    </div>
    <div class="section-body" x-show="open['output']" x-collapse>
      <p>Output sistem adalah <strong>durasi penyiraman</strong> dalam satuan detik (0 &ndash; 300 detik / 0 &ndash; 5 menit).</p>
      <table class="data-table">
        <thead><tr><th>Himpunan</th><th>Tipe</th><th>Parameter</th><th>Rentang Penuh</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>Nol (<em>zero</em>)</td><td>Trapezoidal</td><td>(0, 0, 0, 20)</td><td>0 &ndash; 20</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Pendek (<em>short</em>)</td><td>Triangular</td><td>(10, 60, 110)</td><td>10 &ndash; 110</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Sedang (<em>medium</em>)</td><td>Triangular</td><td>(80, 150, 220)</td><td>80 &ndash; 220</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Panjang (<em>long</em>)</td><td>Triangular</td><td>(180, 240, 280)</td><td>180 &ndash; 280</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Sangat Panjang (<em>very_long</em>)</td><td>Trapezoidal</td><td>(250, 280, 300, 300)</td><td>250 &ndash; 300</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 4. Fungsi Keanggotaan -->
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-header" @click="open['membership'] = !open['membership']">
      <h2>4. Fungsi Keanggotaan</h2>
      <span class="section-arrow" :style="open['membership'] ? 'transform:rotate(90deg)' : ''">&#9654;</span>
    </div>
    <div class="section-body" x-show="open['membership']" x-collapse>
      <p>Sistem menggunakan dua jenis fungsi keanggotaan:</p>

      <div class="subsection">
        <h3>Triangular (a, b, c)</h3>
        <p>Membentuk segitiga dengan puncak di titik <em>b</em>. Nilai keanggotaan = 0 di luar rentang [a, c] dan = 1 di titik b.</p>
        <div class="formula">
          &mu;(x) = 0 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; jika x &le; a atau x &ge; c<br>
          &mu;(x) = (x - a) / (b - a) &nbsp; jika a &lt; x &le; b<br>
          &mu;(x) = (c - x) / (c - b) &nbsp; jika b &lt; x &lt; c
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="subsection">
        <h3>Trapezoidal (a, b, c, d)</h3>
        <p>Membentuk trapesium. Nilai keanggotaan = 1 pada rentang [b, c] dan = 0 di luar [a, d].</p>
        <div class="formula">
          &mu;(x) = 0 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; jika x &le; a atau x &ge; d<br>
          &mu;(x) = (x - a) / (b - a) &nbsp; jika a &lt; x &lt; b<br>
          &mu;(x) = 1 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; jika b &le; x &le; c<br>
          &mu;(x) = (d - x) / (d - c) &nbsp; jika c &lt; x &lt; d
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="note">
        Ketika parameter batas bertemu (misal a = b pada trapezoidal), kurva menjadi "terbuka" di sisi tersebut &mdash; berguna untuk himpunan di ujung rentang seperti "Kering" atau "Basah".
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 5. Basis Aturan -->
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-header" @click="open['rules'] = !open['rules']">
      <h2>5. Basis Aturan (24 Aturan)</h2>
      <span class="section-arrow" :style="open['rules'] ? 'transform:rotate(90deg)' : ''">&#9654;</span>
    </div>
    <div class="section-body" x-show="open['rules']" x-collapse>
      <p>Aturan menggunakan format <strong>IF ... AND ... THEN ...</strong>. Operator AND menggunakan fungsi minimum.</p>

      <div class="subsection">
        <h3>Tanah Kering &mdash; Tanpa Hujan (9 aturan)</h3>
        <table class="data-table">
          <thead><tr><th>#</th><th>Suhu</th><th>Kelembapan Udara</th><th>Durasi Siram</th></tr></thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr><td>1</td><td>Panas</td><td>Rendah</td><td>Sangat Panjang</td></tr>
            <tr><td>2</td><td>Panas</td><td>Sedang</td><td>Sangat Panjang</td></tr>
            <tr><td>3</td><td>Panas</td><td>Tinggi</td><td>Panjang</td></tr>
            <tr><td>4</td><td>Hangat</td><td>Rendah</td><td>Sangat Panjang</td></tr>
            <tr><td>5</td><td>Hangat</td><td>Sedang</td><td>Panjang</td></tr>
            <tr><td>6</td><td>Hangat</td><td>Tinggi</td><td>Sedang</td></tr>
            <tr><td>7</td><td>Sejuk</td><td>Rendah</td><td>Panjang</td></tr>
            <tr><td>8</td><td>Sejuk</td><td>Sedang</td><td>Sedang</td></tr>
            <tr><td>9</td><td>Sejuk</td><td>Tinggi</td><td>Pendek</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <div class="subsection">
        <h3>Tanah Kering &mdash; Hujan Ringan (3 aturan)</h3>
        <table class="data-table">
          <thead><tr><th>#</th><th>Suhu</th><th>Durasi Siram</th></tr></thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr><td>10</td><td>Panas</td><td>Panjang</td></tr>
            <tr><td>11</td><td>Hangat</td><td>Sedang</td></tr>
